data.title: Bruce Hornsby
data.meta_description: Bruce Hornsby. Soundtrack: Backdraft - Männer, die durchs Feuer gehen. Bruce Hornsby was born on 23 November 1954 in Williamsburg, Virginia, USA. He is a composer and actor, known for Backdraft - Männer, die durchs Feuer gehen (1991), Oldboy (2013) and World's Greatest Dad (2009). He has been married to Kathy Lynn Yankovich since 31 December 1983. They have two children.
